data.title: I’m on the road…just walked into a Barnes & Noble. Even after all these years and five books…it is still a thrilling and humbling...
data.meta_description:
39 likes, 3 comments - mikedrobbins on September 27, 2023: "I’m on the road…just walked into a Barnes & Noble.  Even after all these years and five books…it is still a thrilling and humbling experience for me to see one of my books on the shelves in a bookstore next to so many other interesting and inspiring titles.

I remember back when I would wander around stores like this hoping/praying that one day I might be so fortunate to have a book of my own on the shelves.

#Grateful".
